title: Michaelangelo - The Third Kind (01 - 04) (2008) (DCP)
description:
Michelangelo - The Third Kind (01 - 04) (2008) (DCP)


The first issue of this four-part mini-series kicks off during the events that occurred during Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Volume Four #5, specifically the time period immediately following the arrival of the Utrom's 'Moon Island' on Earth. Michelangelo is swept up in the tension and chaos that grips New York in the wake of humanity's first contact with alien life!
